flowchart LR
    U[User bounded receipt prompt] --> UI[Native Claude receipt form]
    UI --> WC[WorkbenchCore materializeClaudeProofSession]
    WC --> D[core-daemon stdio]
    D --> V{Prompt policy}
    V -->|empty or >512 bytes| E[Error response]
    V -->|valid| B[claude-bridge turn-proof]
    B --> P[Claude proof receipt]
    P --> S[session_list upsert]
    S --> T[Read-only Claude receipt timeline]
